<noinclude>
One row of Template:ChapterTable. Receives projected subobject values
via SMW's `format=template | named args=yes`. Emits wikitable row
syntax only (no frame), so the enclosing `ChapterTable` can compose
all rows inside one `{| ... |}`.

The leading newline before `{{!}}-` is load-bearing: SMW concatenates
template invocations with no separator, so without it the row
separator would land on the same line as the previous row's last cell
and MediaWiki's wikitable parser would collapse everything into a
single row.
</noinclude><includeonly>
{{!}}-
{{!}} {{{title|}}}
{{!}} {{{summary|}}}</includeonly>
